Plus, an additional factor was that I'm not sure I'd take well punishments for NOT contributing all I had from other players... Also, at some point I realized that us chatting might decrease our earnings because the waiting time is longer then (the typing player prolongs the waiting time because he is distracted by typing and doesn't submit his money contribution quickly then), so we will have less rounds to earn money then, so I started rushing to do what _I_ can: submit quickly & not trying to write anything in a chat.
